# ShipFlo for WooCommerce
Easily connect your WooCommerce store to **[ShipFlo](https://shipflo.com)** and automate your order fulfillment process.  

This plugin enables automatic order syncing between WooCommerce and your ShipFlo dashboard.
The ShipFlo plugin syncs your WooCommerce orders with the ShipFlo delivery platform, automating dispatch and providing real-time tracking for a hassle-free logistics experience.

---

## ğŸš€ Features

- Automatically push new WooCommerce orders to your ShipFlo account.  
- Display live tracking information for customers.  
- Compatible with popular delivery scheduling plugins.  
- Seamless setup and activation.

