## ğŸ“¦ Order Handling & Automation

- Only **new orders** with **shipping addresses** within ShipFloâ€™s **service areas** are automatically sent to your ShipFlo account.  
- Orders **outside the service area** will remain in WooCommerce.

---

## ğŸ§­ Order Status Updates

### In WooCommerce Admin
- Successfully pushed orders show a **â€œTrack Orderâ€** button.  
- Failed pushes display a **â€œRetry Pushing to ShipFloâ€** button.

### For Customers
- Customers can view real-time **order status updates** on:
  - The **Order Received** page, and  
  - The **My Account â†’ Orders** section.

